Feature:	Calculating Number of Toilet facilities 
			
		
				
			Scenario Outline:	Calculates number of toilet facilities required for a Museum with capacity of 100 people.
			
				Given	user is on "Toilet Calculator" page		
				When	user selects  "Yes" on the radio button on field "Is the number of people for the building known?"		  
				And 	user selects "MUSEUM" from the dropdown on field "Select the building use"
				And		user enters "100" against field "Enter the number of people"
				And 	user clicks on "Submit"
				Then 	details for "Calculated number of toilet facilities" should display
				